findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward(), _getCurrentSupply, _transfer(), and _removeOldSellHistories() use loops that can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there are long lists.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges even after ownership renouncement, allowing them to change various fees, enable/disable buyback, lock/unlock, withdraw tokens and BNBs, set addresses, and more.
